show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/tDTUFR
show.description:
A hilarious tale of love, power, and submission inside a marriage where the rules are flipped.
Between family meddling, ego clashes, and laugh-out-loud twists, nothing is as it seems.
Love, Lies & Laughter is a satirical roller-coaster of drama, betrayal, and comedy that hits home.
